data.description: Move in Ready home near Desert Hawk golf course in Pueblo West! 4 Bed, 3 Bath with a 2 car Garage! Large Living room and Master Bedroom with a spacious walk in closet! The home has a main level laundry,  Tile roof, and Central air!  Enjoy the covered front patio and the large covered area in the back yard perfect for summer barbeques! It would be easy to add 2 more  bedrooms in the basement! Minutes from highway 50.
